SQL: select VEGJOB.REGION as VEGJOB_REGION,VEGJOB.CYCLETYPE as VEGJOB_CYCLETYPE,WPStartDate_Assessment_Xrefs.WP_STARTDATE as WPStartDate_Assessment_Xrefs_WP_STARTDATE,SS.WO as SS_WO,SS.EXT as SS_EXT,VEGSTAT.LINENAME as VEGSTAT_LINENAME,LineIDLookup.FeederID as LineIDLookup_FeederID,STATIONS.STATNAME as STATIONS_STATNAME,UNITS.DESCRIPTIO as UNITS_DESCRIPTIO,VEGUNIT.REMOVCAT as VEGUNIT_REMOVCAT,VEGUNIT.FORESTER as VEGUNIT_FORESTER,VEGUNIT.ASSDDATE as VEGUNIT_ASSDDATE,VEGUNIT.PERMSTAT as VEGUNIT_PERMSTAT,VEGJOB.CONTRACTOR as VEGJOB_CONTRACTOR,JOBVEGETATIONUNITS.NUMTREES as JOBVEGETATIONUNITS_NUMTREES,ISNULL(JOBVEGETATIONUNITS.LENGTHWRK, 0)*3.28084 as JOBVEGETATIONUNITS_LENGTHWRK,JOBVEGETATIONUNITS.ACRES as JOBVEGETATIONUNITS_ACRES,VEGSTAT.FROMSTR as VEGSTAT_FROMSTR,VEGSTAT.TOSTR as VEGSTAT_TOSTR,VEGUNIT.UNIT as VEGUNIT_UNIT,VEGUNIT.AUDIT_USER as VEGUNIT_AUDIT_USER,VEGUNIT.AUDITOR as VEGUNIT_AUDITOR,VEGUNIT.AUDITDATE as VEGUNIT_AUDITDATE,VEGUNIT.AUDIT_FAIL_HIST as VEGUNIT_AUDIT_FAIL_HIST,VEGUNIT.SPECIES as VEGUNIT_SPECIES,SSUNITS.OBJECTID as SSUNITS_OBJECTID,VEGUNIT.ASSNOTE as VEGUNIT_ASSNOTE,VEGUNIT.PARCELCOMMENTS as VEGUNIT_PARCELCOMMENTS,VEGUNIT.AUDIT_PASS as VEGUNIT_AUDIT_PASS,VEGUNIT.UNIT_CLASS as VEGUNIT_UNIT_CLASS,VEGUNIT.ASSLAT as VEGUNIT_ASSLAT,VEGUNIT.ASSLONG as VEGUNIT_ASSLONG,VEGUNIT.COSTMETHOD as VEGUNIT_COSTMETHOD,SSUNITS.GEOMETRY as SSUNITS_GEOMETRY from [SS]  INNER JOIN [VEGJOB] ON (SS.JOBGUID=VEGJOB.JOBGUID)  INNER JOIN [STATIONS] ON (SS.JOBGUID=STATIONS.JOBGUID)  INNER JOIN [SSUNITS] ON (STATIONS.JOBGUID=SSUNITS.JOBGUID AND STATIONS.STATNAME=SSUNITS.STATNAME)  INNER JOIN [VEGUNIT] ON (SSUNITS.JOBGUID=VEGUNIT.JOBGUID AND SSUNITS.STATNAME=VEGUNIT.STATNAME AND SSUNITS.SEQUENCE=VEGUNIT.SEQUENCE)  INNER JOIN [VEGSTAT] ON (STATIONS.JOBGUID=VEGSTAT.JOBGUID AND STATIONS.STATNAME=VEGSTAT.STATNAME)  INNER JOIN [JOBVEGETATIONUNITS] ON (SSUNITS.JOBGUID=JOBVEGETATIONUNITS.JOBGUID AND SSUNITS.STATNAME=JOBVEGETATIONUNITS.STATNAME AND SSUNITS.SEQUENCE=JOBVEGETATIONUNITS.SEQUENCE)  LEFT OUTER JOIN [UNITS] ON (SSUNITS.UNIT=UNITS.UNIT)  LEFT OUTER JOIN [WPStartDate_Assessment_Xrefs] ON (WPStartDate_Assessment_Xrefs.Assess_JOBGUID=SS.JOBGUID)  LEFT OUTER JOIN [LineIDLookup] ON (SS.TITLE=LineIDLookup.LINENAME)  where ((SSUNITS.UNITTYPE =  'VCT' OR SSUNITS.UNITTYPE = 'VAR' OR SSUNITS.UNITTYPE = 'VLG') AND ((SS.EXT = '@')))  AND VEGJOB.WO <> 'x' AND SS.WO = '2025-1930' order by VEGUNIT.ASSDDATE Asc
